docs.lead_paragraph: MONTEVIDEO, Uruguay, March 15 (AP) -- President Jorge Pacheco Areco restored guarantees of constitutional right in Uruguay today. He dropped all controls imposed under a state of emergency nine months ago except for measures designed to check inflation.
